nodes.body: @Forgind can this be merged? https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/pull/6378 depends on arcade latest.

https://devdiv.visualstudio.com/DevDiv/_git/VS/pullrequest/320452 is our latest PR into VS main. It looks like it failed CloudBuild, so I restarted it. @ladipro, if we're good to merge things tomorrow, would you mind merging this and #6361 first?

https://devdiv.visualstudio.com/DevDiv/_git/VS/pullrequest/320452 hit merge conflicts and automation has created https://devdiv.visualstudio.com/DevDiv/_git/VS/pullrequest/320595 in the meantime so I abandoned the former.

Sure, I'll merge #6361 although we're not inserting into VS 17.0 yet so it won't take effect until next week. Please correct me if I'm misunderstanding.
